<p><code class="inline-code">HAggregatorPredicate</code> is used to construct a spline of Hubble H for use in the matching equation. This means we probably <em>always</em> want to run up to the end of inflation, rather than stopping at some point where a largest <code class="inline-code">k</code> mode has just passed outside the horizon (which is what the commented-out logic has in mind).</p>
